Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Inner city decay
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wjkb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Sep 1981
New York power outage highlights nationwide problem of creeping decay of urban infrastructure. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less